    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 36,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "There He makes the hungry dwell, That they may establish a city for a dwelling place,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 36,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 37,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "And sow fields and plant vineyards, That they may yield a fruitful harvest. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 37,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "And sow fields and plant vineyards, That they may yield a fruitful harvest."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 37,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 38,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He also blesses them, and they multiply greatly; And He does not let their cattle decrease. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 38,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He also blesses them, and they multiply greatly; And He does not let their cattle decrease."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 38,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 39,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "When they are diminished and brought low Through oppression, affliction, and sorrow, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
